dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ed8b0d0d41ee0fd854fec2ca3cead07900f104","tid":1972531,"uid":39027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa21947620ceb1c2752fce0ccb3ab71bccbaf1a6","tid":1972531,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"023a5028f05018a8a494f91b5021e07674665cbe","tid":1972531,"uid":39027,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46544587db0717d3dc0482a3d2a6e9b7cc58af46","tid":1972531,"uid":19196,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T23:46:04.000Z","msg":"收租又得<br />\n自主又得<br />\n<br />\n又避到雙重印花稅<br />\n<br />\nYeah <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"用個女個名去收租    又唔使交稅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"一樣要交物業稅的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但已經係最抵既方法<br />\n<br />\n阿媽 買，雙重辣椒<br />\n阿媽 買，雙重辣椒，再轉名比阿女，送契樓一樣要印花稅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:14:55.000Z","msg":"用個人入息課稅報唔係可以扣免稅額咩     仲有D稅務寬減應該分分鐘唔使交"},{"pid":"f5a7568861567f4036aa44ba8af3b52bae085bee","tid":1972531,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f9a0bfd542b959ccf8619e2b405d9357144ac7b","tid":1972531,"uid":315435,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"明明都係20歲，但我仲諗緊點慳聽日三餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:16:47.000Z","msg":"就算你去到50歲,你老豆都唔會變咗個有錢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}